      "writtenOn": "2017-12-12T16:42:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Best thing to do now is to move all of the low-level state in VideoPlayer and Decoder into a VideoPlayerImpl class declared and defined in this .cpp file.\n\nIdeally VideoPlayer would only implement its public interface and refer to VideoPlayerImpl to do everything else.",
      "range": {
