        "id": 1128849
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-12-12T19:33:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If we don\u0027t this, it\u0027s pretty much two classes, a visible and very simple public one, then a private impl class inside the .cpp file. And the public class will be just like a wrapper, calls into the impl. class. The reason is that you are worried that if VideoPlayer.h is included into other .cpp files, too much depencies?",
